Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Nierva Community School in the Municipality of Nabua, Province of Camarines Sur, to Cosme O. Follosco Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 652
An Act Changing the Name of the Nierva Community School in the Municipality of Nabua, Province of Camarines Sur, to Cosme O. Follosco Memorial School
Section 1. The Nierva Community School in the Municipality of Nabua, Province of Camarines Sur, shall hereafter be known as the Cosme O. Follosco Memorial School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
